PN,38601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,FA man who died from cancer was neither
OL,7,Ftold about his diagnosis nor treated
OL,8,Ffor nearly four months due to a
OL,9,F"systemic" failure within Jersey's
OL,10,Fhealth service, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FVictor Charles Francis Tinley, known
OL,13,Fas Vic, had a CT scan at the island's
OL,14,FGeneral Hospital on 24 January 2024,
OL,15,Fwhich detected aggressive, fast-
OL,16,Fgrowing tumours, but he was not
OL,17,Finformed about them until 13 May due
OL,18,Fto a severe communication breakdown.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,FHis results were not immediately
OL,7,Fflagged because the Consultant
OL,8,FHaematologist who requested the scan
OL,9,Fresigned that day and no one else
OL,10,Fpicked it up.
OL,12,FIt was not until a scheduled annual
OL,13,Fcheck-up 15 weeks later that Vic's
OL,14,FLymphoma diagnosis was revealed and he
OL,15,Fbegan treatment.
OL,17,FHe died on 6 January 2025 at Jersey
OL,18,FHospice, aged 84.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,FA serious incident investigation
OL,7,Freport was ordered into the delays in
OL,8,FVic's care and found 11 opportunities
OL,9,Fwhere various doctors could have
OL,10,Fdelivered the news earlier.
OL,12,FNo one was solely responsible for
OL,13,FVic's death, the report concluded, but
OL,14,Fa number of oversights and governance
OL,15,Fissues led to him "falling through the
OL,16,Fcracks".
OL,18,FThe Coroner concluded that these
OL,19,Ffailures contributed to his death.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,FHowever, Vic had previously been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with this type of cancer and
OL,8,Fwas in remission, so health experts
OL,9,Fsay the recurrence is likely to have
OL,10,Fbeen fatal, regardless of whether
OL,11,Fthere had been earlier medical
OL,12,Fintervention.
OL,14,FThe Deputy Viscount, Matt Berry, will
OL,15,Fnow prepare a report for the Health
OL,16,FMinister.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,FHe is expected to call for more
OL,7,Fcollaboration between primary and
OL,8,Fsecondary care providers, so medical
OL,9,Fstaff can promptly and accurately
OL,10,Faccess a patient's notes.
OL,12,FHealth and Care Jersey has accepted
OL,13,Fall of the findings from the review
OL,14,Fand says steps have already been taken
OL,15,Fto address the situation.
OL,17,FIn response, a spokesperson from the
OL,18,Fdepartment adds: "I would like to
OL,19,Fextend my sincere condolences to Mr
OL,20,FTinley's family at this difficult time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,F"As this matter relates to an inquest
OL,7,Fand individual care, it would not be
OL,8,Fappropriate for us to comment on the
OL,9,Fspecifics of the case.
OL,11,F"More generally, work is beginning on
OL,12,Fthe procurement and implementation of
OL,13,Fa shared care record which will bring
OL,14,Ftogether patients' medical information
OL,15,Finto one secure place, that will be
OL,16,Faccessible by GPs, hospital
OL,17,Fclinicians, community teams, and
OL,18,Fmental health and adult social care.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774048278
OL,3,CMan not told about cancer for four
OL,4,Cmonths due to 'systemic' failure
OL,6,F"This will enable faster clinical
OL,7,Fdecisions, fewer gaps in a patient's
OL,8,Fmedical history and less repetition
OL,9,Ffor patients and families."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
